sentences: Gregor van Offeren (born 21 April 1979 in Haarlem, Netherlands), better known as Gregor Salto, is a Dutch DJ and record producer.
Dominating the Dutch club scene for over a decade, Haarlem native Gregor Salto has become famous amongst dance music lovers all across the world.

Having mastered his distinct and versatile sound over the years, Gregor emanates a truly global and exciting blend that fuses elements of soul, Latin-funk and African-grooves laid over a solid base of house and electro four-to-the-floor.
